name: La beauté est un accident nécessaire / from 'My CD Collection'
description: ...as i said in my discord hicathon wg, i lost my comp. it just stopped working. very shortly before that i also lost one. i was computerless. so, i decided to fix that older one. then the repair man burnt the battery. so, we waited for new one to come from the states. in the meantime, i cleaned the house, thoroughly. i arranged my cd collection meticulously. weeks passed by. then i found lil atom with processing 1.5.1 and i just started to draw my cd-s. and that is what i am still doing...
